\nThe 51 mm mortar is a light weapon which can be carried and fired by one man. Smoke, illuminating and high explosive bombs are available. The 51-mm mortar, which replaced the 2-in version, was due to be phased out by the use of the newer 40-mm AG36 UGL (Underslung Grenade Launcher) mounted on the SA-80. However operational experience has led to the decision to replace it with a 60-mm mortar